  "texts": [
    "While no single model wins on all tests, we find that GPT-4o is fairly among the strongest for answering video questions though it is mainly developed for image understanding.",
    "We summarize and outline some of the common findings below, more specific analyses are presented in Sec. 3:",
    "Temporal Understanding: Most Video-LLMs answer temporal questions with high accuracy, but they can hardly reason the order of the video content and are even inferior to non-LLM methods in this regard.",
    "Notably, GPT-4o shows strong temporal reasoning capabilities. 2.",
    "Visual Grounding: Video-LLMs significantly outperform non-LLM methods in answering video questions, but they win marginally in answer grounding."
